      "lang": "javascript",
      "content": "const arr = [5, 8, 13, 21];\nlet found = false;\n\nfor (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i = i + 1) {\n  if (arr[i] === 13) {\n    found = true;\n    break;\n  }\n}\n\nconsole.log(found); // true",
